升级到BitTorrent或μTorrent的Pro版本的用户可以使用下列功能：<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bittorrent.com/bittorrent-plus|title=Delivering the World's Content|accessdate=October 25, 2012|date=|publisher=BitTorrent|archive-date=2014-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141118182933/http://www.bittorrent.com/bittorrent-plus/}}</ref>
